name: Version 1.9
body:
- "Open in Helium" from Safari with the built-in share extension!
- Stays on top even as you switch between spacesâ€”even full screen ones! (This can be disabled in preferences.)
- Navigation gestures like swipe to go back

name: Version 1.8
body: Translucent _always_, on _mouse over_, and _mouse outside_ preference

name: Version 1.6
body:
Renamed menu options and added keyboard shortcuts
Zoom support via menubar, keyboard shortcuts, and trackpad
Added automatic updating

name: Smart URLs!
body: Magically finds pop out youtube and vimeo videos when given the regular URL
Fixed icons and improved first time user experience

This is the initial release of Helium. It supports all the basic features you would expect in addition to some really neat extras such as translucency and mouse event pass-through.
